										<p>
											Note that the inclusion of the 76 m diameter Lovell telescope approximately doubles the sensitivity of the array (except at K-Band),
											however, due to its narrower beam-width, the field of view is approximately halved, depending on the weighting scheme adopted in imaging.
										</p>
										
